## 1. Screen Notifications

When the user asks to add any of the following notifications:
 1. alert
 2. toast
 3. banner
 4. snackbar
 5. dialog

- Always refer to the documentation under "Client Capabilities - Screen Notifications"

- For dialog, always use confirmingActions and dismissingAction, instead of buttons.

